Class InGameLobbyState

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.deib.newdem.adrenaline.controller.InGameLobbyState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LobbyState

    public class InGameLobbyState
extends java.lang.Object
implements LobbyState
    Lobby state that represents a lobby hosting an ongoing game. No new users are accepted and new users cannot modify the lobby state.
